    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>pork</strong> <strong>mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) with your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong>, <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix thoroughly with clean hands until fully combined, then shape into 6 <strong>meatballs </strong>per person and reboil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>",
